# MCP Usage Guidelines

## General Rules

- After MCP tasks, create cursor rules for reuse to reduce failures
- Check cursor rules before tasks; use MCP when available
- If MCP is required but inaccessible, ask to check settings

## Best Practices

- Always verify MCP availability before attempting operations
- Create reusable Cursor Rules after successful MCP operations
- Document MCP configuration issues for troubleshooting and add to the rules for future usage